    <title>Hexo Blog搭建笔记</title>
    <url>/2020/04/27/blogbuilding/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h3 id="2020-04-27"><a href="#2020-04-27" class="headerlink" title="2020.04.27"></a>2020.04.27</h3><p>第一次将blog部署到github 并设置了个人域名</p>
<h3 id="2020-04-28"><a href="#2020-04-28" class="headerlink" title="2020.04.28"></a>2020.04.28</h3><p>使用了NexT主题<br><img src="/2020/04/27/blogbuilding/2.png" class=""><br><a id="more"></a></p>
